{"tid":747214,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"入唔到windows 又assess唔到啲files","createTime":"2018-07-18T08:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T19:03:38.000Z","uid":92750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4da23785867ad3d62c4c19a776862893a81e7641","tid":747214,"uid":92750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"本身電腦有兩個HDD，每隻一個windows。早兩日無啦啦入唔到windows 10，一直都係白色波波係到碌。今朝又入到去另一個畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/155446_e4397ee81e5109df01ecb2236bc04b7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F155446_e4397ee81e5109df01ecb2236bc04b7c.png&h=ca6fb7e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nClose咗佢就會重新開機，再入番依個畫面無限loop 。<br />\n<br />\n咁揀boot 另一個HDD，就係win7黎，入到windows，但係想揀番win10啲使用者檔案出黎就唔得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/160043_3550de78d90eff198c01b7f141050f65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F160043_3550de78d90eff198c01b7f141050f65.png&h=1b8fa36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n箭咀指住果條bar就load好耐都未load完<br />\n㩒繼續就無反應<br />\n啲重要嘅相同文件就save哂係依個folder入面<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以拎到啲檔案出黎呢？"},{"pid":"398e6a0de68008c3e9c613655d429691abab0e79","tid":747214,"uid":99642,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"俾返部機人啦"},{"pid":"a74ec39d40c55be13c566872b8830124a0ec2651","tid":747214,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"繼續 等一陣呢? 都係無反應?"},{"pid":"361c5ed2f6b9023db8aedc305fce9fd3090aa7f0","tid":747214,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398e6a0de68008c3e9c613655d429691abab0e79","tid":747214,"uid":99642,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"俾返部機人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"笑點？"},{"pid":"bdffce6d66f5068dcbeb4441267e0649da2e3c2a",